        <mxCell id="note" value="&lt;b&gt;One-way coupling.&lt;/b&gt; Data flows physical &#8594; digital only. No actuation back to the vessels or environment, so per Kritzinger et al. (2018) this is strictly a &lt;i&gt;digital shadow&lt;/i&gt;." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fontSize=11;fillColor=#FFFFCC;strokeColor=#cccc00;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
